descriptionHtml:
As you step through the gates of Markarth make a 90 degree turn to the right and back in the corner is your new home, Blackwood Manor.
Once belonged to a Dwemer Prince and now its yours.

Contains:
12 chests
126 weapon plaques
43 mannequins
2 female mannequins standing by your throne
1 large bed
2 small beds
1 strong box

And as a show of respect for your status as the Dovahkiin the Jarl as lend you 3 low security prisoners to do chores around the manor.
author: Godeepblue
